                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/inthefields/">龙在田</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-05-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">著作是典籍，必不可少；而课堂讲述如心法，只能言传面授。《论语》部分打5星；文话部分略微零散而且重复处稍多。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1134266229">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1134266229" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1134266229" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1134266229">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kidcby/">狷介有乌青</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-01-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">【2017.4】先知道叶嘉莹，后找了这本书，文以载道，能得顾随先生亲自授课实乃一大幸事</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

