              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39907333/" class="">第3页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/marysays/" class=" " title="而已">而已</a>
                (今朝风日好，或恐有人来)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="39907333">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39907333/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p39907333-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">曾子战战兢兢，喜欢自省，顾随认识到这样的人容易得抑郁症啊，老是自责。

</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-10-28 10:28</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                曾子战战兢兢，喜欢自省，顾随认识到这样的人容易得抑郁症啊，老是自责。
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p39907333-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>

                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







